book:

    Hibernate Tools

    Reference Guide



Version: 1.0.0.GA













    Preface


Hibernate Tools is a toolset for Hibernate 3 and related projects.
    The tools provide Ant tasks and Eclipse plugins for performing reverse
    engineering, code generation, visualization and interaction with
    Hibernate.


